{"id": "1385266046738632775", "channel_id": "1385266046738632775", "type": 0, "author_id": "883992032530563082", "author_name": "void_1546.", "author_bot": false, "content": "發現pvp裡的命輪沒有人仔細的介紹，所以就來介紹所有的命輪\n分為多篇，本篇為R級命輪篇\n純個人主觀看點，歡迎補充\n\n以下正文", "timestamp": "2025-06-19T14:32:42.541000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1385266046738632775", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位對弈命輪介紹（R級篇）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1385266939596898334", "channel_id": "1385266046738632775", "type": 0, "author_id": "883992032530563082", "author_name": "void_1546.", "author_bot": false, "content": "洞悉\n算力消耗：3\n\n效果：獲得對方首次打出的指令卡（除打擊）並且算力消耗減一，每回合至多一次。\n\n介紹：基本能夠穩定的在每回合獲得一張牌，由於是對方首次打出的指令卡，因此會有許多的不穩定性，獲得的指令卡視為裝備者的卡，因此享受裝備者的正面效果（強化、強效等），也吃負面效果（虛弱、強效降低等），推薦給非主C角穿戴或擁有傷害成長能力的角色。", "timestamp": "2025-06-19T14:36:15.415000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1385266939357564999", "filename": "IMG_3961.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 841279, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1385266046738632775/1385266939357564999/IMG_3961.png?ex=69cbdbdf&is=69ca8a5f&hm=8c66716f2ded60a38ac0cd9bdaaf4c4791f1bd1339a7495156ee0690a8966600&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1385266046738632775", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位對弈命輪介紹（R級篇）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
