{"id": "1385267492146118769", "channel_id": "1385266046738632775", "type": 0, "author_id": "883992032530563082", "author_name": "void_1546.", "author_bot": false, "content": "熟成\n\n算力消耗：2\n\n效果：回合結束後獲得一張可以給予任意我方角色10點狂氣的牌，若已有回10點狂氣的牌，將其合成成為回20點狂氣的牌。\n\n介紹：獲得可支配的狂氣，可以加速我方任意角色狂氣回轉，推薦給非主C角穿戴。", "timestamp": "2025-06-19T14:38:27.153000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1385267492233936986", "filename": "IMG_3959.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 879620, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1385266046738632775/1385267492233936986/IMG_3959.png?ex=69cbdc63&is=69ca8ae3&hm=3ead79caa4cf1f0cd68745ed4c3ec64eb7eb634ee7d3b24782e10c29e57fd505&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1385266046738632775", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位對弈命輪介紹（R級篇）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
